title: Spaceship Pass-By Sound Effects
description: Professionally Designed Spaceship Pass-By & Fly-By Sound Effects including small and fast pass-bys, medium-sized ones, and massive cargo cruiser and mothership pass-by sci-fi sound effects!
longDescription:
Youtube Demo: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pp877EHYWaQ


Spaceship Pass-Bys sound library contains professionally designed, high quality spaceship pass-by sound effects that will perfectly fit into any production featuring futuristic, hi-tech vehicles and space travel sci-fi scenes!


From fast and small spaceship fly-bys, medium-sized ones, all the way to the massive cargo cruisers and gigantic mothership pass-by sounds, from bursty and energetic pass-bys to the smooth-sounding gliding ones, these cutting edge spaceship sound effects will sonically immerse your audience into a futuristic, hi-tech world of tomorrow and bring the scenes with futuristic spacecrafts and advanced sci-fi vehicles to life!


On top of 200 pass-bys, the library comes with 40 hand-picked source sounds created with synthesizers and noise generators that are used extensively as layers during the sound design process and creation of this library, useful for all kinds of sci-fi whoosh & transition sounds and movements, hi-tech futuristic vehicles sound effects, etc!


If you like the sound of Spaceship Pass-Bys then you might also like New Horizons ansd Sci-Fi Whooshes sound libraries!


Spaceship Pass-Bys Sound Effects List
